The paper discusses the creation of a large-scale Chinese knowledge graph that is technology-oriented and built from technical papers published in Chinese academic journals. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Machine Learning (cs.LG), or Databases (cs.DB) sub-categories of arXiv CS.
